                     <interp inst="t18180114-5-person93" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at No. 10, Belton-street, Longacre. I know all the three prisoners, but they did not live in the same house with me. I was sitting in a room at No. 10, where I live, and the three prisoners came into the room with the desk, about a quarter before six o'clock in the evening. It was a small mahogany desk with brass handles-
               <persName id="t18180114-5-person94">
                  Sarah 
                  Wilson
               <interp inst="t18180114-5-person94" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180114-5-person94" type="given" value="Sarah"></interp>
